!! Introduction
Would you rather...

* be famous when you are alive and forgotten when you die or be unknown when you are alive but famous after you die?
* give up bathing for a month or give up the internet for a month?
* have a horrible job, but be able to retire comfortably in 10 years or have your dream job, but have to work until the day you die?
* be rich or be stoned to death?
* live a pleasant life or die by the sword?
* be respected or be beheaded?

Acts 7 we see Stephen die by stoning.

For what purpose do we do these things? I assume they would be like Paul.

